notes.p: "Use of Model-Based Compartmental Analysis and a Super-Child Design to Study Whole-Body Retinol Kinetics and Vitamin A Total Body Stores in Children from Lower-Income Countries" by Jen Ford and friends (2020)
The original model was coded in WinSAAM. There the delay compartments were modelled as a series of connected pseudo-compartments. We use the same approach here.
The model includes a helper parameter EXPERIMENT. Setting EXPERIMENT=1 simulates Bangladesh, EXPERIMENT=2 simulates Philippines, EXPERIMENT=3 simulates Guatemala.
